{"tid":1632813,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要比佢哋見下惡報（慎入）","createTime":"2019-10-06T23:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T18:33:13.000Z","uid":125434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acefa13ed67e2f38c4eb57e2723b16ca101eb28d","tid":1632813,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T23:31:44.000Z","msg":"對家已經完全唔理啲人點樣鬧佢地，等於你落到球場上重覆嘅垃圾話講太多人哋其實都唔會受到影響，屌佢只係嘥口水，不如下次直接印啲圖出嚟，或者播住一啲同報應有關嘅聲帶，係另一種心理層次上嘅影響<br />\n<br />\n另外泰國地獄公園呢啲圖都可以拎嚟做文宣，有好多時撕紙狗係知道自己唔係正義，佢哋只係冇諗過作惡嘅後果，咁就要更加比佢哋知道做仆街嘅下場，從心理上不斷影響佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuatixo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyuatixo.jpg&h=2412ca3c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oq2b0LO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foq2b0LO.jpg&h=b8d70f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZptnnZb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZptnnZb.jpg&h=85048602&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vscfHZi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvscfHZi.jpg&h=023589ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/He1oRSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHe1oRSQ.jpg&h=1790f459&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKhzd6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKhzd6f.jpg&h=bad8eb94&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOMoRSW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOMoRSW.jpg&h=98f0d8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAJZqc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYAJZqc1.jpg&h=c9bf123e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be515b537c8ee003d43037f601d18c35bffe204f","tid":1632813,"uid":125434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06